B5AUD.original: ~z~ones who worry, and ones who go down.
B5_BH
B5_DE
~z~Understood... I'm a little on edge here. We got a real problem. Jimmy wants you to handle this.
B5AUD.translated: ~z~懂吗...我没有地位。我们有一个难题。Jimmy希望你去处理。

B5AUD.original: ~z~Great, I gotta go get noticed so I ain't a suspect.
B5AUD.translated: ~z~好，我去别的地方露露脸，省得被人怀疑。

B5AUD.original: B5_BC
~z~Fuck you. Even if you take me out,
B5_HA
B5_DA
B5_CG
~z~Motherfuuuuuuuuccccckkkkker!
~z~I mean, I ain't raising them, and I ain't seeing them,
B5AUD.translated: ~z~我说，我可不会养着他们，更不会去看他们，

B5AUD.original: ~z~Right.
~z~The fucking Russians have got to Charlie Matteo.
~z~This fucking chopper better not crash. Shit.
B5AUD.translated: ~z~这破直升机最好别掉下来。操。

B5AUD.original: ~z~Can't be a close friend, know what I mean.
B5AUD.translated: ~z~别做亲密的朋友，想想我说的话。

B5AUD.original: B5_EC
B5_BF
~z~Everyone on the Commission is gonna want Jimmy P clipped after this.
B5AUD.translated: ~z~从今往后，所有委员会成员都会想做掉Jimmy P的。

B5AUD.original: ~z~Blow up the fucking bridge... make it look real ugly.
B5AUD.translated: ~z~炸烂这破桥...给他们看看真正的邪恶。

B5AUD.original: B5_CH
B5_FA
B5_BI
~z~Chubby Charlie's gonna live to eat another canolli.
B5AUD.translated: ~z~肥佬Charlie想活着去再吃些卡诺里。

B5AUD.original: B5_FB
B5_DC
~z~Decisions... decisions.
~z~Jimmy P's taken it too far this time. He's over.
B5AUD.translated: ~z~Jimmy P实在是太过分了。他死定了。

B5AUD.original: B5_CE
B5_FC
B5_AA
B5_CC
~z~Cause I been hearing things, things I don't like...
B5AUD.translated: ~z~因为我听到了一些事情，一些我不喜欢的事情...

B5AUD.original: ~z~You're finished. All the Pegorinos is dog food.
B5AUD.translated: ~z~你的工作完成了。所有Pegorino家族都已经做成狗粮了。

B5AUD.original: ~z~He is about to take a chopper into Algonquin to share that knowledge with the Commission.
B5AUD.translated: ~z~马上他就要乘直升机去Algonquin，把这事上报委员会了。

B5AUD.original: B5_CB
B5_JA
~z~We shoulda whacked all them low rate Alderney hoods a long time ago.
B5AUD.translated: ~z~我们早应该狠揍那群低能的Alderney佬。

B5AUD.original: B5_BA
~z~I may be getting whacked, but at least I don't employ no low rate hoods like you.
B5AUD.translated: ~z~我也许会受到打击，但至少我不会雇佣你这种败类。

B5AUD.original: ~z~Okay.
~z~Great, Jimmy P sent one of his low rate goons to try and clip me. Good luck, asshole!
B5AUD.translated: ~z~好啊，Jimmy P派了个三流打手来杀我。祝你好运，混蛋！

B5AUD.original: ~z~I thought Phil Bell had Jimmy P under control. They've gone over the edge.
B5AUD.translated: ~z~我想Phil Bell已经被Jimmy P控制住了。他们已经越界了。

B5AUD.original: B5_KA
B5_BE
B5_BG
B5_BB
~z~That's a real shame.
B5_EA
B5_HB
~z~Go to the old factory off of Argus Street.
~z~Jimmy wants you to hit the meeting while he and I are publicly at dinner.
B5AUD.translated: ~z~Jimmy希望你去破坏这场会面，他和我会在公开场合吃晚餐。

B5AUD.original: ~z~What has to happen is that you gotta take out Chubby Charlie before he choppers it into Algonquin
B5AUD.translated: ~z~当务之急是在肥佬Charlie飞到Algonquin前把他做掉。

B5AUD.original: B5_HC
~z~You don't need to worry about the fat man singing. He's lost his voice.
B5AUD.translated: ~z~你不用担心那个胖子去告密了，他说不了话了。

B5AUD.original: ~z~I'm coming back to clip you, asshole. Don't worry about that.
B5AUD.translated: ~z~我会回来干掉你的，混蛋。不必担心。

B5AUD.original: ~z~With all respect, that's not my business. I'm the hired help
B5AUD.translated: ~z~恕我直言，与我无关。我只是临时工。

B5AUD.original: ~z~I don't think so. You're pretty paranoid.
~z~You immigrant scumbag. In my prime I coulda turned you inside out.
B5AUD.translated: ~z~你是个卑鄙的偷渡客。我要是还年轻非把你干掉不可。

B5AUD.original: ~z~my chopper pilot's gonna take the message straight to the Commission.
B5AUD.translated: ~z~我的直升机驾驶员也会把消息送去委员会的。

B5AUD.original: ~z~I'm outta here. Next stop the fucking Commission.
B5AUD.translated: ~z~拜拜啦您。下一站，狗屁委员会。

B5AUD.original: B5_GA
~z~A capo named Benny is going to be meeting with the Russians. They're gonna convince him to go to war.
B5AUD.translated: ~z~一个叫Benny的小头目将会与俄国佬见面。他们会劝说他参战。

B5AUD.original: ~z~No, paranoia is when you worry about things unnecessarily...
B5AUD.translated: ~z~不，偏执狂不是你现在必须担心的事情...

B5AUD.original: ~z~to tell the Commission that we're knocking off the Ancelottis' action.
B5AUD.translated: ~z~别让委员会知道我们在搅合Ancelotti家族的生意。

B5AUD.original: ~z~I'll leave it up to you. See you later.
~z~but I'd like to think that when my ex-wife stops wanting to have me killed herself, maybe I'll be part of their lives.
B5AUD.translated: ~z~但我想，如果我前妻不再想要我自杀了，可能我会成为他们生活的一部分。

B5AUD.original: B5_CF
~z~What's the world coming to if low rate hoods like you is being used for muscle?
B5AUD.translated: ~z~如果让像你这样的贱货拥有权力，那这世界会变成什么鬼样子？

B5AUD.original: ~z~I'll do my best to shut him up then.
~z~So, I go into this factory and I ice this Fat Charlie?
B5AUD.translated: ~z~所以我先进这家工厂，再把这个胖Charlie给干掉？

B5AUD.original: ~z~Somehow, Chubby Charlie Matteo has found out it was us who ripped off the Russian coke.
B5AUD.translated: ~z~肥佬Charlie Matteo居然知道了是我们劫走了俄国人的可卡因。

B5AUD.original: ~z~Jimmy P is finished. Fucking finished!
~z~Cause I been hearing things, things I don't like, things will get someone hurt.
B5AUD.translated: ~z~因为我听到了一些事情，一些我不喜欢的事情，一些会给我们带来伤害的事情。

B5AUD.original: ~z~Hey Niko... let's go for a walk.
~z~The Commission is gonna have a chuckle about this.
~z~This family is about to get dysfunctional.
~z~One lesson I've learnt, Niko. Assume everyone knows everything.
B5AUD.translated: ~z~我得到了一个教训，Niko。若要人不知，除非己莫为。

B5AUD.original: ~z~That's right, I'm gonna go make a lot of noise so no one thinks I had anything to do with it.
B5AUD.translated: ~z~没错，我就去别处搞点动静，制造不在场证据。

B5AUD.original: ~z~So, if you see Ray, if you speak to him, remind him, someone's gonna get hurt.
B5AUD.translated: ~z~所以，如果你认识Ray，如果你责备他、提醒他，有的人将会受伤。

B5AUD.original: ~z~And you want it hit hard?
~z~How about them swingers, eh? Great work man, great work.
B5AUD.translated: ~z~浪人队的比赛怎么样了？干得好啊，兄弟，干得好。

B5AUD.original: ~z~Chubby Charlie Matteo ain't someone you wanna piss off.
~z~Okay, let's go, c'mon, quick. We gotta head towards Port Tudor.
B5AUD.translated: ~z~那好，出发，行动，快。我们现在就要去Tudor港。

B5AUD.original: ~z~Did you see a blue van parked nearby as you drove here? Back on Lyndon Avenue?
B5AUD.translated: ~z~你开车来的时候看到一辆蓝色厢型车停在附近？回Lyndon Avenue？

B5AUD.original: ~z~Next time I see the Peg, he'll be wearing cement boots.
B5AUD.translated: ~z~下次见到Peg的时候，他就该穿着水泥靴*了。~n~(字面意思，将活人沉江用的工具)

B5AUD.original: B5_CD
~z~You burst in the front and hit them in the face with everything you got.
B5AUD.translated: ~z~正面突击，火力全开，面对面交火。

B5AUD.original: B5_BD
~z~You want me to take this fat man out before that happens?
B5AUD.translated: ~z~你想让我在这个胖子上报前把他干掉？

B5AUD.original: ~z~You remember that sugar we borrowed... well the Russians ain't too pleased. They're convinced it was down to Jimmy.
B5AUD.translated: ~z~你还记得我们借来的毒品吗...俄国佬可不是很乐意。他们确信是Jimmy搞的鬼。

B5AUD.original: ~z~They told this top Ancelotti Capo that it was us that took the sugar.
B5AUD.translated: ~z~他们告诉了这个Ancelotti家族最大的组长，是我们抢走了货。

B5AUD.original: ~z~Otherwise you slip around the back, go in through the basement and fuck them up their asses.
B5AUD.translated: ~z~要不然，绕到他们后面，走地下室进去，爆了他们的菊花。

B5AUD.original: ~z~Every time. I don't want that. I got kids.
B5AUD.translated: ~z~每次都是。我不想这样。我有孩子。

B5AUD.original: ~z~Shit, Phil. The fat man is on his way to Algonquin. I couldn't get him.
B5AUD.translated: ~z~妈的，Phil。胖子已经在去Algonquin的路上了，我无能为力了。

B5AUD.original: ~z~No, I don't think so.
~z~Did you see a fuckin' helicopter on your way here?
B5AUD.translated: ~z~来的路上有没有看见直升机？

B5AUD.original: ~z~No.
~z~Of course.
~z~Who knows how the fuck they knew.
~z~Come see me.
~z~Ahhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhh!
~z~You ain't fit to lick my spats.
B5_IA
~z~Not only is we gonna be looking over our shoulders every two seconds but we ain't gonna be able to earn.
B5AUD.translated: ~z~时刻担心自己人头落地也就算了，我们连钱都没得赚了。

B5AUD.original: B5_ED
~z~I didn't tell nobody.
~z~I'm sorry to hear that.
~z~Alright, now the way I sees it there's two ways it can go down.
B5AUD.translated: ~z~好了，据我观察，现在有两种行动方案。

B5AUD.original: ~z~Of course but they don't know that and we don't want them convincing the Ancelottis either.
B5AUD.translated: ~z~他们当然不知道，我们也不想他们说服那些Ancelottis佬。

B5AUD.original: ~z~trust me, I been in this game long enough to know there's two kind of wise guys...
B5AUD.translated: ~z~相信我，我在这场游戏中参与了很久，我知道有两种聪明人...

B5AUD.original: ~z~Maybe the ones who don't worry, act all crazy, maybe they get to the top for a bit, frighten a few people.
B5AUD.translated: ~z~可能那些人并不担心，行动却是很疯狂，也许他们达到了顶峰，吓到了一些人。

B5AUD.original: ~z~If you don't then it'll be the Pegorinos going to the mattresses with every one of the Liberty City families.
B5AUD.translated: ~z~如果干不掉他，就等于Pegorino家族和所有自由城的家族开战了。

B5AUD.original: B5_EB
B5_CA
~z~It don't matter.
B5_DB
~z~They end up dead or inside within three years.
~z~It's no big deal... has Ray been talking shit? About me?
B5AUD.translated: ~z~那不是大问题...Ray还说了什么浑话？有没有关于我的？

B5AUD.original: ~z~It was.
~z~This ain't good. I gotta tell Jimmy P.
B5_DD
